SUMMARY:Hayhurst Invitational - Mountain State Innovators Summit
DESCRIPTION:The summit aims to bring together youth\, college students and early-stage entrepreneurs for hands-on coaching\, meaningful networking and real-world opportunities. There is a total of $300\,000 in prizes and awards!  There are competition categories for middle school\, high school\, veteran-specific\, women-focused products\, undergrad\, graduate\, and brick-and-mortar businesses and more!
